reviewText: Doctor in the house had one Welsh intern.  I learned two things.  I can speak Welsh and the Welsh intern became my very favorite actor.  Most famous now for the curly headed Professionals Ray Doyle.  Even at age 70 now he is still foxy!
Loved the humor of St. Swithins and the student doctors.  Just wish that they had the DVDs able to be viewed in the US.  doctor.
